Print for an evoverse dataset.

Source: R/S3_methods_print.R
print.mbst_data.Rd

The print reports basic statistics on the stored fits available in the input object.

# S3 method for mbst_data
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An evoverse object.
...

S3 parameters

Value

Nothing.

Examples

data('example_evoverse')
print(example_evoverse)
